ntiment analysis <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sentiment_analysis>.=E2=80=
=9D =0AIf the prose is cheerful, perhaps you figure that=E2=80=99s a good s=
ign and buy the =0Astock; if it=E2=80=99s not, you don=E2=80=99t.=0A=0AEnou=
gh people do some form of this (computerized sentiment analysis, or just =
=0Areading the press releases and getting a vibe) that:=0A=0A * A stock wil=
