if it=E2=80=99s gloomy, even if the substance is the same, and =0A * Compan=
ies know this and have some incentive to be cheerful, though it is =0Acount=
erbalanced by their =E2=80=9Ceverything is securities fraud=E2=80=9D incent=
ive to be =0Agloomy to avoid getting sued.=0AWhich reduces the value of the=
